::Prowl::

Prowl roars again as he feels Iron Raptor jerking his foot down. His 
claws were still jammed into her back, but they slide out as Prowl 
loses stability in the air and falls. He spins around on his way 
down, jerking his foot out of her grasp and sinking his front claws 
into Iron Raptor's back again, his teeth bitting at her neck.
